responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D27B64DE4E03FEBDD974E8863A786AEB", "You\'ll need some acid webbing, an eye of dregehorn, kirin blood and the rarest part, and most important a loch of the witch\'s hair before she was cursed.  You then mix those in the witch\'s cauldron and it\'ll produce a cloud that will bring her down to your level. ")
